narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: YES. The class is a lot of fun, and not that much work (compared to L1-L4 Japanese, I hear). Hiroe-sensei is knowledgeable of a variety of topics and is very funny. His teaching style also makes it easy to befriend your (3 or 4) classmates.
I would definitely recommend this class to anyone who is interested in sharpening his Japanese linguistic skills and learn about Japanese lifestyle and culture! It is indeed a great class.

This course is a great class if you want to continue your advanced study of Japanese language. Even after having taken a number of advanced Japanese language courses I still learned a lot from this course, and itis worth it just to have the opportunity to take one of Hiroe Sensei's classes.
